        <content type="html" xml:base="https://nikhilkulkarni1109.github.io/projects/itilite-sage/">&lt;p&gt;Think of it as our DIY version of &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.glean.com&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Glean&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We indexed all internal docs (Google Docs, Sites, Confluence) into a vector DB.
Added a few common user profiles like Support, Tech, PMs, and Founders, and used system prompts + RAG to give useful answers with links to the right docs.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founders and customer support teams used it to pull insights from sales calls and customer chats.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
